WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue(c.color9CD5FF) { color: #9CD5FF; }
::cue(c.colora8c7fa) { color: #a8c7fa; }

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:07.000 line:0
<b><c.color9CD5FF>One Pace Premium</c></b>
Keep the project alive: <c.colora8c7fa>ko-fi.com/not6ip</c>

2
00:00:17.330 --> 00:00:20.540
Did you know there's an awesome treasure at the end of this sea?!

3
00:00:20.540 --> 00:00:23.340
And whoever gets it becomes King of the Pirates!

4
00:00:23.340 --> 00:00:24.960
Isn't that exciting?!

5
00:00:24.960 --> 00:00:28.010
Cool new adventures are waiting out there!

6
00:00:30.400 --> 00:00:38.060
BON VOYAGE! Hitokakera no yuuki hirogete
BON VOYAGE! Light the ember of courage and let the fire grow

7
00:00:38.060 --> 00:00:45.660
Mirai he no SHIPPO chotto mieta yo
I caught a glimpse at what's beyond the horizon

8
00:00:45.780 --> 00:00:48.210
Back when we first started

9
00:00:45.780 --> 00:00:53.430
Saisho wa minna BARABARA ni egaite ita chiheisen

10
00:00:48.210 --> 00:00:53.430
we had separate ideas about where we would soon go

11
00:00:53.740 --> 00:00:55.380
Things have changed now,

12
00:00:53.740 --> 00:01:00.440
Ima nara hitotsu no bouenkyou de nozokeru

13
00:00:55.380 --> 00:01:00.440
when we look towards our dreams we all share one telescope

14
00:01:00.730 --> 00:01:05.680
When you find that your heart's been led astray

15
00:01:00.730 --> 00:01:09.980
Kimi no KOKORO madowasu unmei no shoppai KONPASU

16
00:01:05.680 --> 00:01:09.980
time to calibrate your compasses

17
00:01:09.980 --> 00:01:13.010
Sakate ni kaji toru yo
Set a new course, turn the tables now

18
00:01:13.010 --> 00:01:20.300
BON VOYAGE! SHIGARAMI mo kako mo sutete
BON VOYAGE! Shed your previous baggage, forget the past

19
00:01:20.300 --> 00:01:27.140
Bokura nara sore demo waraeteru hazu
Smiles can weather a storm, we know that better than anyone

20
00:01:27.140 --> 00:01:29.080
Don't you fret,

21
00:01:27.140 --> 00:01:34.900
Yume wo kanaeru tame no namida naraba

22
00:01:29.080 --> 00:01:34.900
tears shed along the way to your dreams are not in vain

23
00:01:34.900 --> 00:01:41.100
Oshiku wa nai PRECIOUS IN MY LIFE
You know that you're all PRECIOUS IN MY LIFE

24
00:01:42.060 --> 00:01:49.210
Mirai he no SHIPPO chotto mieta yo
I caught a glimpse at what's beyond the horizon

25
00:01:49.670 --> 00:01:52.970
Conis

26
00:01:52.970 --> 00:01:55.890
Oh? Are you bringing that with you?

27
00:01:57.180 --> 00:01:58.390
Well...

28
00:01:59.180 --> 00:02:01.980
If I can't, then...

29
00:02:02.980 --> 00:02:07.730
I don't think you'll be needing it
where we're going, but all right.

30
00:02:07.730 --> 00:02:09.110
Do as you wish.

31
00:02:10.280 --> 00:02:12.650
Th-Thank you!

32
00:02:12.650 --> 00:02:15.280
I-I really like this thing, so...

33
00:02:30.510 --> 00:02:32.550
Are you concerned about them?

34
00:02:32.550 --> 00:02:33.840
Oh, no...!

35
00:02:34.840 --> 00:02:37.600
There's no need to hold back.

36
00:02:37.600 --> 00:02:44.190
They were but cretins who couldn't
understand the power of a god,

37
00:02:44.190 --> 00:02:45.770
unlike you.

38
00:02:46.600 --> 00:02:51.280
Frankly, a mind that can't be
controlled by fear...

39
00:02:51.280 --> 00:02:53.280
can be so troublesome at times.

40
00:02:53.280 --> 00:02:54.780
Wouldn't you agree?

41
00:02:54.780 --> 00:02:56.280
Y-Yeah...

42
00:02:56.280 --> 00:02:58.120
You're right.

43
00:03:04.580 --> 00:03:07.250
I can't let him notice.

44
00:03:07.250 --> 00:03:09.630
I have no choice but to obey him.

45
00:03:09.630 --> 00:03:12.710
I need to be ready
to escape at any moment!

46
00:03:12.710 --> 00:03:13.970
Until then...

47
00:03:38.360 --> 00:03:39.240
Whoa...

48
00:03:39.870 --> 00:03:41.580
What is this...?

49
00:03:44.370 --> 00:03:46.790
It's natural to be awestruck.

50
00:03:46.790 --> 00:03:48.540
There is only one in the world.

51
00:03:48.540 --> 00:03:51.880
A ship that I alone can control.

52
00:03:53.670 --> 00:03:56.630
After all, it's powered by lightning.

53
00:03:57.510 --> 00:03:59.340
Is that possible?

54
00:03:59.340 --> 00:04:01.680
It only requires my abundant energy

55
00:04:01.680 --> 00:04:07.810
and a conduit material
to transmit the necessary charge.

56
00:04:08.140 --> 00:04:11.520
A material that can transmit energy?

57
00:04:16.320 --> 00:04:18.070
Precisely.

58
00:04:18.070 --> 00:04:21.570
The gold that laid
waiting on this island.

59
00:04:21.570 --> 00:04:24.950
The people down below
should feel blessed.

60
00:04:24.950 --> 00:04:31.290
They get to witness
a rare spectacle before they die.

61
00:04:34.170 --> 00:04:35.800
A flying ship?!

62
00:04:35.800 --> 00:04:37.420
I can't believe it!

63
00:04:37.420 --> 00:04:42.890
If it really can fly, I won't have
an opportunity to escape!

64
00:04:46.770 --> 00:04:48.890
This is the Ark Maxim.

65
00:04:48.890 --> 00:04:52.610
With this ark, we shall
reach that boundless land...

66
00:04:52.610 --> 00:04:55.270
the Endless Vearth!

67
00:05:43.660 --> 00:05:45.410
We're out...

68
00:05:45.410 --> 00:05:47.290
We finally made it out...

69
00:05:49.120 --> 00:05:51.250
The ground is stone...

70
00:05:51.250 --> 00:05:53.460
What is this place?

71
00:05:58.170 --> 00:06:00.130
Did you see something?!

72
00:06:02.630 --> 00:06:04.840
Hey! Answer me!

73
00:06:06.470 --> 00:06:08.680
Luffy!

74
00:06:13.350 --> 00:06:14.770
We're out!

75
00:06:15.810 --> 00:06:18.110
We made it out!

76
00:06:19.610 --> 00:06:21.490
Check it out! Where are we?

77
00:06:21.490 --> 00:06:22.610
It looks like ruins.

78
00:06:23.110 --> 00:06:26.620
So it's here? The huge golden bell?

79
00:06:28.120 --> 00:06:32.750
Could this place be... our homeland?

80
00:06:32.750 --> 00:06:34.750
Oh? What's that?
There's a huge hole...

81
00:06:38.130 --> 00:06:39.170
Luffy!

82
00:06:39.170 --> 00:06:41.960
Wait! What is it this time?!

83
00:06:42.760 --> 00:06:45.930
Where are you going?!

84
00:06:48.760 --> 00:06:50.430
Zoro!

85
00:06:50.430 --> 00:06:52.890
Hey! Snap out of it!

86
00:06:54.270 --> 00:06:55.850
How could this happen...

87
00:06:56.650 --> 00:06:58.560
with you here?!

88
00:07:05.360 --> 00:07:06.660
Nami...!

89
00:07:06.660 --> 00:07:08.820
Where's Nami?! She's not here!

90
00:07:08.820 --> 00:07:10.790
Wyper!

91
00:07:11.990 --> 00:07:13.290
Even Wyper...!

92
00:07:15.290 --> 00:07:17.920
It's that bazooka guy...

93
00:07:17.920 --> 00:07:19.540
He's really strong, but even so...

94
00:07:19.540 --> 00:07:21.250
Who did this to everyone?!

95
00:07:22.420 --> 00:07:24.220
Enel did!

96
00:07:25.220 --> 00:07:27.430
He's the only one...

97
00:07:29.890 --> 00:07:32.010
who's capable of doing this.

98
00:07:37.440 --> 00:07:39.860
Enel... Is he that god guy?

99
00:07:39.860 --> 00:07:40.940
Yes...

100
00:07:40.940 --> 00:07:45.150
My mantra didn't work
while we were inside the snake,

101
00:07:45.150 --> 00:07:48.450
so I don't know
what happened here, but...

102
00:07:51.280 --> 00:07:52.030
Robin!

103
00:07:54.540 --> 00:07:56.160
Miss Navigator...

104
00:07:57.040 --> 00:07:59.000
was taken away.

105
00:07:59.790 --> 00:08:00.750
H-Hey, wait!

106
00:08:01.250 --> 00:08:02.500
Take it easy!

107
00:08:02.880 --> 00:08:06.340
Was Nami taken by that god guy?

108
00:08:06.340 --> 00:08:07.680
Where?!

109
00:08:07.680 --> 00:08:08.970
I don't know.

110
00:08:09.550 --> 00:08:11.220
Listen carefully...

111
00:08:12.050 --> 00:08:14.220
The way things stand...

112
00:08:14.770 --> 00:08:17.060
this nation, Skypiea, will disappear.

113
00:08:17.060 --> 00:08:19.270
Huh?! The sky island...?!

114
00:08:20.650 --> 00:08:22.650
Our village, too?!

115
00:08:24.280 --> 00:08:26.110
Everything...

116
00:08:26.780 --> 00:08:30.070
He said that he'd return
everyone in the sky...

117
00:08:30.450 --> 00:08:32.320
to the ground.

118
00:08:43.420 --> 00:08:49.380
So Enel is gonna head for
the golden bell, right?

119
00:08:49.970 --> 00:08:52.720
Yes. I'm sure he's going there.

120
00:08:52.720 --> 00:08:55.470
But if you take too long
and fail to find them in time,

121
00:08:55.470 --> 00:08:57.810
you won't get a second chance...

122
00:08:57.810 --> 00:08:59.440
Don't worry!

123
00:09:00.230 --> 00:09:01.810
I know where they are.

124
00:09:01.810 --> 00:09:04.150
There are two voices
moving on this island.

125
00:09:05.230 --> 00:09:07.690
It must be Nami and Enel!

126
00:09:12.570 --> 00:09:13.660
Aisa.

127
00:09:18.950 --> 00:09:21.370
Take me to them!

128
00:09:23.630 --> 00:09:26.090
I can see Angel Island...!

129
00:09:28.210 --> 00:09:30.340
Attention everyone, heso!

130
00:09:31.180 --> 00:09:34.720
The wickedly profane
Pagaya and his daughter,

131
00:09:34.720 --> 00:09:39.100
along with their accomplice, Gan Fall,
the former god, are on the run!

132
00:09:39.100 --> 00:09:41.600
Please be careful!

133
00:09:42.350 --> 00:09:47.590
If you see the criminals,
please alert me, McKinley, immediately!

134
00:09:47.620 --> 00:09:50.860
I repeat, alert me,
McKinley, immediately!

135
00:09:50.860 --> 00:09:52.820
In the name of God Enel,

136
00:09:52.820 --> 00:09:58.240
we, the White Berets,
will protect Skypiea's peace!

137
00:09:58.240 --> 00:09:59.330
– Heso!
– Heso!

138
00:09:59.660 --> 00:10:02.120
Report! I have a report!

139
00:10:03.500 --> 00:10:04.750
What's the matter?

140
00:10:04.750 --> 00:10:06.590
Yes, sir! You see...

141
00:10:06.590 --> 00:10:07.840
What?!

142
00:10:07.840 --> 00:10:10.550
Pagaya's daughter
has appeared at the harbor?!

143
00:10:25.940 --> 00:10:29.070
The blasphemer has entered Gate 1!

144
00:10:29.070 --> 00:10:30.440
Why?

145
00:10:30.440 --> 00:10:33.700
Does she want to be captured?!

146
00:10:33.700 --> 00:10:36.070
Don't let her get away!
Capture her at any cost!

147
00:10:38.950 --> 00:10:40.540
Bring it on, criminal!

148
00:10:44.290 --> 00:10:47.170
Please get out of my way!

149
00:10:52.460 --> 00:10:54.590
What're you doing?! Out of my way!

150
00:10:57.680 --> 00:11:00.640
Why me...?

151
00:11:01.020 --> 00:11:03.850
– Captain!
– Captain!

152
00:11:11.280 --> 00:11:13.030
– Captain!
– Captain!

153
00:11:21.910 --> 00:11:23.040
N-No...

154
00:11:23.370 --> 00:11:25.080
Captain McKinley!

155
00:11:25.080 --> 00:11:26.040
It's the criminal!

156
00:11:26.040 --> 00:11:27.670
It's the woman who defied God!

157
00:11:27.670 --> 00:11:28.420
Stay away!

158
00:11:28.420 --> 00:11:30.000
God's reckoning is coming!

159
00:11:38.390 --> 00:11:40.510
What an enormous amount of gold...

160
00:11:40.510 --> 00:11:42.640
Remember that girl
from Angel Beach?

161
00:11:42.640 --> 00:11:48.060
It sounds like she's causing
quite a scene on Angel Island.

162
00:11:48.060 --> 00:11:49.940
Conis?! It can't be...

163
00:11:49.940 --> 00:11:52.230
She should be on our ship!

164
00:11:52.570 --> 00:11:56.320
There's a lot of commotion
going on outside, too.

165
00:11:56.320 --> 00:12:00.070
However, there are
more pressing matters...

166
00:12:03.410 --> 00:12:08.120
Th-That mantra ability you all have...

167
00:12:08.920 --> 00:12:11.630
It can even identify individuals?

168
00:12:11.630 --> 00:12:15.590
I wouldn't say it's perfect.

169
00:12:15.590 --> 00:12:18.340
But it's special in my case.

170
00:12:19.680 --> 00:12:21.640
In addition to my unique mantra,

171
00:12:21.640 --> 00:12:27.020
I can also hear conversations by using
my lightning power to detect sound waves.

172
00:12:27.020 --> 00:12:31.980
If I hear even one word
of blasphemy, I bestow my reckoning.

173
00:12:31.980 --> 00:12:36.190
As long as it's happening within
this nation, it's a simple matter.

174
00:12:36.190 --> 00:12:37.820
So that's why...

175
00:12:37.820 --> 00:12:41.490
It certainly is an ability
fit only for a god.

176
00:12:43.580 --> 00:12:46.750
Try as hard as you like to run
and escape, people of the sky.

177
00:12:46.750 --> 00:12:49.040
This is the end of Skypiea!

178
00:12:49.040 --> 00:12:52.330
A party with angels
dancing in the sky!

179
00:12:53.460 --> 00:12:55.090
Say, girl.

180
00:12:55.090 --> 00:13:00.590
Have you ever seen the faces of those
who suddenly lose their footing?

181
00:13:02.690 --> 00:13:04.180
What am I gonna do?!

182
00:13:04.180 --> 00:13:06.560
If I don't escape now...

183
00:13:06.560 --> 00:13:11.560
No... Even if I manage to escape,
the sky island will be gone...

184
00:13:11.560 --> 00:13:13.150
What can I do?!

185
00:13:14.480 --> 00:13:15.320
U-Um...

186
00:13:16.900 --> 00:13:18.490
Is something wrong, sir?!

187
00:13:21.570 --> 00:13:22.990
Who is that?

188
00:13:23.820 --> 00:13:26.540
No... it's nothing.

189
00:13:30.370 --> 00:13:33.170
Please... Please listen
to what I have to say!

190
00:13:34.290 --> 00:13:35.920
Stay back! Don't come near us!

191
00:13:35.920 --> 00:13:38.550
Everyone, please listen!

192
00:13:38.550 --> 00:13:40.220
There's no time to lose!

193
00:13:40.220 --> 00:13:43.140
Please! Calm down and hear me out!

194
00:13:43.140 --> 00:13:44.930
Shut up! Stay back!

195
00:13:44.930 --> 00:13:47.560
Leave the island, you plague!

196
00:13:47.560 --> 00:13:51.310
Yeah! With you around, we'll also
be struck by God's reckoning!

197
00:13:51.310 --> 00:13:52.140
You heretic!

198
00:14:00.360 --> 00:14:01.780
Don't come near me!

199
00:14:03.530 --> 00:14:05.280
This is a flame bazooka.

200
00:14:06.580 --> 00:14:07.830
I'll shoot!

201
00:14:12.120 --> 00:14:15.830
Everyone, please! Get to the edge
of the clouds right away! To Cloud End!

202
00:14:15.830 --> 00:14:17.420
Escape to the Blue Sea!

203
00:14:18.170 --> 00:14:21.300
This nation is about to disappear!

204
00:14:21.300 --> 00:14:23.550
There is no time to waste!

205
00:14:23.550 --> 00:14:27.930
Use every boat there is
and escape Angel Island!

206
00:14:28.470 --> 00:14:30.720
What is she babbling about...?

207
00:14:32.600 --> 00:14:36.110
God Enel intends
to erase this nation!

208
00:14:36.110 --> 00:14:38.820
If you stay here, you'll all die!

209
00:14:40.480 --> 00:14:41.690
Don't be ridiculous!

210
00:14:41.690 --> 00:14:43.110
What're you trying to pull?!

211
00:14:43.110 --> 00:14:44.240
Is this revenge?!

212
00:14:44.240 --> 00:14:46.120
You're taking this nonsense too far!

213
00:14:46.120 --> 00:14:48.370
Do you want us to be punished, too?!

214
00:14:49.410 --> 00:14:51.370
Don't insult God Enel!

215
00:14:54.120 --> 00:14:55.210
I'm sorry...

216
00:15:09.890 --> 00:15:11.140
What?

217
00:15:11.140 --> 00:15:12.350
She dropped her weapon?!

218
00:15:15.190 --> 00:15:16.520
Hey! Capture her!

219
00:15:15.810 --> 00:15:16.520
Yes, sir!

220
00:15:16.520 --> 00:15:17.690
I...

221
00:15:17.690 --> 00:15:18.310
I...

222
00:15:18.310 --> 00:15:22.320
I renounce Enel as god!

223
00:15:22.320 --> 00:15:23.240
I renounce Enel as god!

224
00:15:23.240 --> 00:15:27.660
I renounce Enel as god!

225
00:15:30.410 --> 00:15:31.580
Father...

226
00:15:37.080 --> 00:15:38.130
This is bad!

227
00:15:38.130 --> 00:15:38.920
Hurry, run!

228
00:15:38.920 --> 00:15:40.920
Evacuate! Evacuate!

229
00:15:40.920 --> 00:15:43.010
God's reckoning is coming!

230
00:15:58.850 --> 00:16:00.310
Huh?

231
00:16:00.310 --> 00:16:01.060
Strange...

232
00:16:01.440 --> 00:16:03.150
Her reckoning wasn't delivered.

233
00:16:03.150 --> 00:16:04.150
Why...?

234
00:16:04.150 --> 00:16:08.280
But… she openly
insulted God himself…

235
00:16:09.870 --> 00:16:11.700
What's going on...?

236
00:16:11.700 --> 00:16:15.160
As you can see, it no longer matters
whether I am eliminated.

237
00:16:15.160 --> 00:16:17.710
"Skypiea will be eradicated."

238
00:16:17.710 --> 00:16:20.460
A member of the Holy Host
escaped Upper Yard,

239
00:16:20.460 --> 00:16:23.840
risking his life to deliver
that message to all of you.

240
00:16:23.840 --> 00:16:24.550
He...

241
00:16:25.760 --> 00:16:28.970
He received God's reckoning,
along with my father.

242
00:16:32.430 --> 00:16:34.180
What did she say about God?

243
00:16:34.180 --> 00:16:35.270
What?!

244
00:16:35.890 --> 00:16:38.310
Doesn't God help us?

245
00:16:38.770 --> 00:16:40.770
What's she saying?

246
00:16:41.900 --> 00:16:43.570
There's no time to lose.

247
00:16:43.570 --> 00:16:46.900
Everyone, evacuate
to Cloud End immediately!

248
00:16:46.900 --> 00:16:47.740
It can't be...

249
00:16:48.570 --> 00:16:50.110
H-Hold on a second!

250
00:16:50.110 --> 00:16:50.740
Huh?

251
00:16:50.740 --> 00:16:53.490
Don't be ridiculous!
We can't leave just like that!

252
00:16:53.490 --> 00:16:56.620
We were born and raised
in this sky! After all these years...

253
00:16:56.620 --> 00:16:58.160
That's right!

254
00:16:58.160 --> 00:17:01.080
We've never even been
to the Blue Sea!

255
00:17:01.080 --> 00:17:03.340
How could we live there? Besides...

256
00:17:03.340 --> 00:17:05.880
So you're just going to
wait here to die?!

257
00:17:06.460 --> 00:17:10.970
For the past six years, you've gotten
to know the kind of man Enel is.

258
00:17:10.970 --> 00:17:15.470
Once he commits to something,
he always follows through!

259
00:17:15.470 --> 00:17:16.310
If you still–

260
00:17:16.310 --> 00:17:18.230
But it may not happen!

261
00:17:18.230 --> 00:17:19.940
Perhaps there could be a miracle...

262
00:17:20.480 --> 00:17:22.650
and this sky island could still survive.

263
00:17:22.650 --> 00:17:24.520
Y-Yeah.

264
00:17:24.520 --> 00:17:26.150
God could change his mind.

265
00:17:26.150 --> 00:17:27.360
Yeah...

266
00:17:27.360 --> 00:17:28.320
If that happens...

267
00:17:47.840 --> 00:17:50.590
What we know better than anything...

268
00:17:51.010 --> 00:17:54.970
is that he has the power to cast us
into despair at any moment!

269
00:17:54.970 --> 00:17:58.810
Well, that moment draws near!

270
00:17:58.810 --> 00:18:02.560
We can't keep waiting
for a miracle to happen!

271
00:18:02.940 --> 00:18:06.520
Right now, there is no
divine power in this country!

272
00:18:07.230 --> 00:18:08.530
Before you pray...

273
00:18:08.900 --> 00:18:13.110
Before you turn a blind eye to reality,
you have to do what you can!

274
00:18:13.700 --> 00:18:17.240
The days when you could
lay low and survive are over!

275
00:18:17.240 --> 00:18:18.540
You have to take action!

276
00:18:18.990 --> 00:18:22.870
Blaming someone later
won't save your lives now!

277
00:18:25.790 --> 00:18:26.630
So...

278
00:18:27.460 --> 00:18:29.210
make the decision to leave!

279
00:18:32.380 --> 00:18:33.550
Escape to the Blue Sea!

280
00:18:33.550 --> 00:18:34.510
Grab your things!

281
00:18:34.510 --> 00:18:35.470
To Cloud End!

282
00:18:35.470 --> 00:18:36.350
Do as she says!

283
00:18:36.350 --> 00:18:37.550
Get to Cloud End!

284
00:18:37.550 --> 00:18:38.180
Hurry up!

285
00:18:38.180 --> 00:18:40.520
There's no time to waste!

286
00:18:42.640 --> 00:18:43.730
Excuse me!

287
00:18:44.100 --> 00:18:46.480
Do you know what happened
to the Holy Host?!

288
00:18:46.480 --> 00:18:49.020
My husband is in the Host.
I want to escape with him!

289
00:18:49.020 --> 00:18:50.860
My son is in it, too!

290
00:18:50.860 --> 00:18:52.490
Are the Holy Host members okay?!

291
00:18:52.490 --> 00:18:55.660
My son, too! My only son left
for duty and hasn't come back yet!

292
00:18:54.360 --> 00:18:55.660
Um... well...

293
00:18:57.570 --> 00:18:59.330
The Holy Host is probably...

294
00:18:59.910 --> 00:19:02.120
I don't know...

295
00:19:02.120 --> 00:19:05.000
What has the Holy Host been
forced to do for all this time?

296
00:19:05.000 --> 00:19:06.080
Where are they?!

297
00:19:06.080 --> 00:19:08.210
Isn't there anything you can tell us?

298
00:19:11.170 --> 00:19:15.510
We, the White Berets, will look into
the matter of the Holy Host!

299
00:19:15.510 --> 00:19:19.180
We'll have them catch up
with all of you later!

300
00:19:19.180 --> 00:19:21.140
Please go. There's no time!

301
00:19:21.140 --> 00:19:22.600
Captain McKinley...

302
00:19:22.600 --> 00:19:24.270
Hurry and leave!

303
00:19:24.270 --> 00:19:25.100
Captain!

304
00:19:26.100 --> 00:19:29.060
I can guess what fate
awaits the Holy Host.

305
00:19:30.020 --> 00:19:32.530
I know the kind of man Enel is.

306
00:19:32.530 --> 00:19:34.570
I'm certain of it.

307
00:19:34.570 --> 00:19:39.570
However, the evacuation of this island
and its people is our top priority.

308
00:19:39.570 --> 00:19:41.790
I won't let this become another Birka.

309
00:19:41.790 --> 00:19:42.830
Birka...?

310
00:19:42.830 --> 00:19:47.540
A sky island in the far southeast
where Enel was born and raised.

311
00:19:47.540 --> 00:19:51.590
I heard that it disappeared
without a trace six years ago.

312
00:19:51.590 --> 00:19:53.550
Six...? Don't tell me...

313
00:19:53.550 --> 00:19:54.550
That's right.

314
00:19:54.550 --> 00:19:58.510
Enel destroyed his homeland
and came to this nation.

315
00:19:59.470 --> 00:20:02.060
I heard Birka had
strong warriors as well,

316
00:20:02.060 --> 00:20:04.640
but they were nothing against Enel.

317
00:20:05.350 --> 00:20:06.940
He's invincible. He's a "god."

318
00:20:08.810 --> 00:20:11.310
It may be true.

319
00:20:11.770 --> 00:20:13.650
You might already know,

320
00:20:13.650 --> 00:20:18.450
but we were also members
of Gan Fall's Holy Host.

321
00:20:18.450 --> 00:20:22.080
We believed that by appearing
to betray the Holy Host

322
00:20:22.080 --> 00:20:26.540
and obeying Enel, we could stay on
the island and protect these people.

323
00:20:27.080 --> 00:20:31.250
What a pathetic plan
that turned out to be!

324
00:20:31.710 --> 00:20:34.710
We tried to make sure
no one would rebel against God,

325
00:20:34.710 --> 00:20:38.090
or at least that no one
would anger him.

326
00:20:38.090 --> 00:20:39.550
That was all we could do!

327
00:20:40.180 --> 00:20:45.470
Shameful! Shameful!
How utterly shameful!

328
00:20:47.890 --> 00:20:49.390
I don't think so.

329
00:20:51.060 --> 00:20:53.860
Thank you for telling me the truth.

330
00:20:55.030 --> 00:20:56.070
Captain...

331
00:20:56.650 --> 00:20:59.700
Um... can I ask you
to take care of the people here?

332
00:20:59.700 --> 00:21:02.030
Of course, but where are you going?

333
00:21:02.030 --> 00:21:05.660
Well, there are a few people who
don't know the escape route.

334
00:21:05.660 --> 00:21:06.750
They're my friends...

335
00:21:07.370 --> 00:21:08.710
I have to go back.

336
00:21:09.250 --> 00:21:10.580
Thank you!

337
00:21:12.670 --> 00:21:14.420
Oh, the Blue Sea people...

338
00:21:16.050 --> 00:21:16.710
– Heso!
– Heso!

339
00:21:19.420 --> 00:21:20.380
Heso!

340
00:21:41.200 --> 00:21:43.700
I'm not sure I can carry everyone...

341
00:21:45.410 --> 00:21:47.330
Regardless, we need to...

342
00:21:48.410 --> 00:21:50.710
escape to the upper area somehow.

343
00:22:00.220 --> 00:22:01.720
Aisa!

344
00:22:01.720 --> 00:22:04.050
You're sure it's this way, right?!

345
00:22:04.050 --> 00:22:06.300
Yeah! We're very close!

346
00:22:06.300 --> 00:22:07.890
I'm sure of it!

347
00:22:07.890 --> 00:22:08.720
Okay!

348
00:22:12.850 --> 00:22:16.820
That's it! Luffy! The hole
on the left! That's the place!

349
00:22:16.820 --> 00:22:18.190
That's the place?!

350
00:22:18.190 --> 00:22:19.780
Alright!

351
00:22:28.790 --> 00:22:33.330
As I thought, it seems there were
more than five survivors on this island...

352
00:22:33.330 --> 00:22:37.460
Honestly... where could
they possibly have been hiding?

353
00:22:37.460 --> 00:22:38.300
Could it be...?

354
00:22:44.510 --> 00:22:46.390
How aggravating...

355
00:22:47.260 --> 00:22:50.470
So my prophecy did not come true.

356
00:22:52.730 --> 00:22:57.190
Are you that Enel guy?!

357
00:23:08.910 --> 00:23:11.330
Luffy!

358
00:23:12.540 --> 00:23:15.210
What have you been doing...

359
00:23:15.210 --> 00:23:16.580
to my friends?!

360
00:23:18.630 --> 00:23:20.460
Which pieces of filth, exactly?

361
00:23:20.800 --> 00:23:22.460
Stay right there!

362
00:23:22.460 --> 00:23:23.970
I'm gonna come kick your ass!

363
00:23:23.970 --> 00:23:25.840
Mind your tongue!

364
00:23:25.840 --> 00:23:27.720
I am God!

365
00:23:27.720 --> 00:23:30.140
What makes you a god?!

366
00:23:30.140 --> 00:23:33.600
He's picking a fight with Enel big time.

367
00:23:33.600 --> 00:23:35.890
Are you gonna be okay, Luffy?

368
00:23:36.600 --> 00:23:38.770
H-Hey, Luffy! Be caref–

369
00:23:43.610 --> 00:23:47.160
I can hear it now,
the party of angels...

370
00:23:47.160 --> 00:23:50.580
It seems that the flock
has learned of Skypiea's fate.

371
00:23:52.120 --> 00:23:55.960
I wonder how far they'll get before
the ground falls beneath their feet.

372
00:23:55.960 --> 00:23:57.120
Like I said...

373
00:23:57.120 --> 00:23:59.880
what makes you a god?!

374
00:24:00.920 --> 00:24:02.000
You shall see...

375
00:24:08.510 --> 00:24:09.930
I get it now...

376
00:24:09.930 --> 00:24:13.060
You're no ordinary human, either.

377
00:24:13.060 --> 00:24:15.890
But as a lowly paramecia…

378
00:24:15.890 --> 00:24:17.390
you haven't got a chance!

379
00:24:18.560 --> 00:24:22.230
Before me, all is futile!

380
00:24:22.980 --> 00:24:25.490
Hence, I am God.

381
00:24:27.490 --> 00:24:28.200
El...

382
00:24:29.660 --> 00:24:31.070
Thor!

383
00:24:33.030 --> 00:24:34.450
Luffy!

384
00:24:39.120 --> 00:24:40.540
Luffy...

385
00:24:41.380 --> 00:24:42.880
Oh, no...

386
00:25:02.810 --> 00:25:05.570
Well done, dodging that attack...

387
00:25:05.570 --> 00:25:07.280
60 Million Volts...

388
00:25:07.280 --> 00:25:08.740
What?! Dodged it?!

389
00:25:09.110 --> 00:25:11.110
Thunder Serpent!

390
00:25:25.380 --> 00:25:26.840
100 Million Volts...

391
00:25:27.710 --> 00:25:28.840
Vari!

392
00:25:32.260 --> 00:25:33.390
Of course...

393
00:25:33.390 --> 00:25:36.100
It makes sense
when you think about it!

394
00:25:36.100 --> 00:25:38.310
Luffy is immune to lightning...

395
00:25:38.770 --> 00:25:40.270
because he's rubber!

396
00:25:40.270 --> 00:25:41.980
That's...

397
00:25:41.980 --> 00:25:44.770
enough!

398
00:26:01.040 --> 00:26:02.420
Calm down!

399
00:26:02.420 --> 00:26:05.790
Physical attacks can't affect me!

400
00:26:05.790 --> 00:26:07.670
Come on, this Blue Sea monkey i–

401
00:26:11.840 --> 00:26:15.720
His lightning power
is completely ineffective!

402
00:26:15.720 --> 00:26:19.560
Just the idea of a human who's
unaffected by lightning...

403
00:26:19.560 --> 00:26:23.310
is something even Enel
himself could never imagine.

404
00:26:30.530 --> 00:26:34.410
Could it be that Luffy is Enel's...

405
00:26:34.410 --> 00:26:36.620
one and only natural enemy?!
